Mail-Foundry version 0.08
=========================

Mail::Foundry creates an API for MailFoundry servers using LWP to
authenticate and post form data.

This module is no longer actively maintained. Only working patches
will be accepted for maintenance.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  LWP
  URI::Escape
  HTML::Form

